RoboScope Browser Recorder Extension
=====================================

This Chrome extension is based on robotframework-recorder v0.7.0
(https://github.com/viadee/robotframework-recorder), a Chrome browser
extension that records user actions and scans web pages to generate
Robot Framework test script templates.

robotframework-recorder is itself a fork of Robotcorder
(https://github.com/sohwendy/Robotcorder) by @sohwendy.

Original Authors:
  - @sohwendy (Robotcorder)
  - @xylix (robotframework-recorder / Robocorp Recorder)
  - viadee Unternehmensberatung AG

License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)
See the LICENSE file in this directory for the full license text.

This modified version adds RoboScope integration capabilities,
allowing the extension to communicate with a RoboScope server
instance for enhanced recording, AI-powered keyword optimization,
and direct test file management within RoboScope projects.

The RoboScope core application (backend/ and frontend/ directories)
is licensed under Apache License 2.0 and does not contain any code
from this extension. Communication between the extension and
RoboScope occurs exclusively via HTTP/WebSocket APIs.
